data.description: Beautiful home, like NEW (built in 2020), bright, airy, and spacious; 4 bedrooms + huge BONUS room, 3 full bathrooms; Approximately 2,265 Sq Ft.   The owner’s suite is on the main floor with separate walk-in tile shower and spacious tub, walk-in closet, double sink vanity.  Kitchen features granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances; 9 FT ceilings on the main level, fireplace, Trane® HVAC system w/ Dual-Zones (two thermostats) , fireplace, double pane windows, covered patio. Extra wide driveway with yard access, huge lot, cul-de-sac and more.
